    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. so it sounds like the \"benefits\" might be a bit of a stretch for a shop like mine then. if you had to weigh it all up, do you think these wage hikes are actually doing more harm than good for rural economies, or is there a way they actually work out in the long run?",
